 \sum_{k=n-m}^{n-1} \frac{k \sin \frac{k \pi}{n}}{1 + \cos^2 \frac{k \pi}{n}} = \sum_{k=1}^{m} \frac{(n-k) \sin \frac{k \pi}{n}}{1 + \cos^2 \frac{k \pi}{n}}. 
