 \lim_{n\to\infty} \sum_{k=1}^{n} \frac{\frac{k}{n} \sin \frac{k \pi}{n}}{1 + \cos^2 \frac{k \pi}{n}} \frac{1}{n} = \frac{1}{\pi^2} \int_{0}^{\pi} \frac{x \sin x}{1 + \cos^2 x} \, dx = \frac{1}{4}. 
